WEBVTT

00:03:56.014 --> 00:04:01.612
Architecture is the built expression
of those changes.

00:04:02.347 --> 00:04:06.674
So, this is why it is so difficult,

00:04:07.411 --> 00:04:11.836
because those changes create adventure.

00:04:12.514 --> 00:04:15.244
They create adventure,
and architecture is adventure.

00:04:15.268 --> 00:04:18.934
This is the Centre
Georges Pompidou in Paris,

00:04:18.958 --> 00:04:20.133
a long time ago.

00:04:20.459 --> 00:04:23.777
That was back in time, '77.

00:04:24.623 --> 00:04:29.170
This was a spaceship
landing in the middle of Paris.